channel.title: [317]Chris-Scape V1 (Customs! Open Source & Client! 33.8k+ Views & 10000+ DL's!)
channel.description: Ok everyone. I have been starting on a new project, officially named Chris-Scape, and it is my first version. I am new to coding, and I am still learning, so V2 will be MUCH more exciting. But, first of all, I will start off with the Credits. [b]40% to God Pure (for source)[/b] [b]10% to RuneXC (for client)[/b] [b]50% to me (for coding and editing the server)[/b] Next, here are the client and source links! [center][b][i][u]Source[/u][/i][/b] Megaupload: http://www.megaupload.com/?d=K9DTQQEC Uppit: http://uppit.com/v/PHH224YY[/center] [center][b][i][u]Client[/u][/i][/b] Megaupload: http://www.megaupload.com/?d=IINN9BB1 Uppit: http://uppit.com/v/JXFX3FG8[/center] [center][b]Features of Chris-Scape V1:[/b] ~New Home Area, With New Custom Models (Thanks RuneXc) ~New Custom Sprites Added By Me ~Shops Moved, Will Move In V2, Too Cramped Right Now ~New Skills Area ~New Vengeance Emote, Shows Actual Red Skull Like RuneScape And Does Correct Emote ~New GodWars, With General Graardor, Commander Zilyana, Kree'arra, and K'ril Tsutsaroth ~New Pking Area, Now In Lumbridge (PVP Style) ~More Shops Also Moved, Not Clumped Together, Located In Desert ~Gsmini, Same As Always, Will Fix In V2 ~New 3rdAge Area, Now In Secret Room ~New Training Area With New Models ~Barrows, Kill Each Brother To Advance, Then Use Key On Chest For Reward ~New Slayer Area, Kill Monsters For Exp, New Models Added Here As Well ~Santa Land, Easy Training, Drop Baubles ~KBD, Drops Wide Variety Of Items ~Corporal Beast, New Model, New Area, Drops GodWars Items ~All SkillCape Emotes[/center] [b][i][u]Pictures!!! (Features Also)[/u][/i][/b] [b]Home Area, New Sprites, and Customs! (Of course, there's more!)[/b] [IMG]http://i40.tinypic.com/72v9qw.jpg[/img] [b]Summoning Works! The follow as well![/b] [IMG]http://i43.tinypic.com/34j80af.jpg[/img]
